<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Hayot yoĘ»ling va soĘ»zlaring koĘ»rsat bizga</title>
<key>Dm</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
.Dm               C          Bb
 Hayot yoĘ»ling va soĘ»zlaring koĘ»rsat bizga,
.C           Bb           Am      Dm
 Mashaqqatli,olov yoĘ»ldan oĘ»tkaz bizni.
.Dm               C          Bb
 Men yolvorib gar chaqirsam eshit meni,
.C           Bb         Am       Dm
 Yuragimda Muqaddas Ruh ulugĘ»lab Seni.

[V2]
 Imon qayigĘ»in tebratadi toshqin daryo,
 Shu toĘ»fonda ham kaloming sochar ziyo.
 Gar boĘ»lmasang imon uchun OĘ»zing qoya,
 Bor kuchimla tirishsamla ketar zoye.

[V3]
 Bu dunyoning tashvishlari yoĘ»lim toĘ»sar,
 Lek imonim kalomingla bagĘ»rim oĘ»sar.
 Qoldirmaysan bu hayotda meni Ozing,
 YoĘ»l ochadi bu gĘ»ovlardan faqat soĘ»zing.</lyrics>
</song>